00:12:57.420 --> 00:13:01.220
What does that framework
that gives us permission

00:13:01.380 --> 00:13:03.180
to dream look like in the US?

00:13:04.140 --> 00:13:07.580
Here's a component
to the US legal framework.

00:13:07.700 --> 00:13:11.460
We have federal laws, national laws,
that apply across the whole country.

00:13:11.700 --> 00:13:14.340
We have regulations based on those laws.

00:13:14.500 --> 00:13:17.020
We have policy statements
from the government.

00:13:17.100 --> 00:13:21.980
There are state laws
in all 50 states.

00:13:22.140 --> 00:13:26.260
Many states have accessibility
or disability inclusion laws.

00:13:26.620 --> 00:13:29.860
We even have local laws
in some cities and some counties.

00:13:29.980 --> 00:13:32.300
Then we have implementation of all that.

00:13:32.380 --> 00:13:35.260
That all works together,
which is why I have a picture here

00:13:35.380 --> 00:13:39.060
