00:22:43.980 --> 00:22:48.060
I encourage you to check those out
if you're in that sector or you're interested.

00:22:48.380 --> 00:22:50.700
I have to say one other quick thing here.

00:22:51.500 --> 00:22:54.780
These federal agencies,
they are not buildings.

00:22:54.940 --> 00:22:57.860
The people who work
in them are not robots.

00:22:58.020 --> 00:23:02.820
As probably all over the world,
