00:24:22.420 --> 00:24:27.620
One sort of hot topic is, can you file
a lawsuit about a web-only business?

00:24:27.780 --> 00:24:29.820
You'll see if you're on social media,

00:24:29.980 --> 00:24:33.860
there was a recent case last week
where a court in New York said,

00:24:33.980 --> 00:24:36.980
"In this court,
you can no longer file web-only."

00:24:37.100 --> 00:24:40.020
It has to be connected
in some way to a physical space.

00:24:40.220 --> 00:24:42.180
Like, you have a retail store,

00:24:42.300 --> 00:24:45.140
