for the disabled person.

00:46:48.700 --> 00:46:52.900
In the US, usually you have
to pay your own lawyer,

00:46:53.020 --> 00:46:56.660
but in discrimination cases
like race, gender, disability,

00:46:56.740 --> 00:46:59.900
the rule
is that the fee requirement shifts.

00:47:00.060 --> 00:47:01.300
They call it fee shifting.

00:47:01.460 --> 00:47:03.580
If a company discriminates,

00:47:03.700 --> 00:47:07.060
